title: Week 5 NFL Recap: Dak Prescott suffers devastating injury, Alex Smith returns, Dan Quinn fired (Football 10/12)
description:
Will Brinson, Ryan Wilson and John Breech link up to break down all the Sunday action from Week 5 of the 2020 NFL season. The guys start by discussing the gruesome injury that Dak Prescott suffered vs. the Giants and what it means for his future. They are certainly unfortunate circumstances, but it's now up to Breech's boy Andy Dalton to lead America's Team. Meanwhile, Alex Smith completed his miraculous comeback and Dan Quinn has been fired. For real this time. Full breakdown below.
Cowboys-Giants (3:00)
Rams-Washington (20:15)
Vikings-Seahawks (27:15)
Panthers-Falcons (35:15)
Raiders-Chiefs (40:00)
Dolphins-49ers (52:45)
Steelers-Eagles (59:30)
Browns-Colts (1:11:00)
Ravens-Bengals (1:20:00)
Texans-Jaguars (1:25:30)
Cardinals-Jets (1:30:00)
Winners/Losers
